<p class="ayah 38-23" id="23" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَـٰذَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">this</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَخِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) my brother,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he has</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تِسْعٌ وَتِسْعُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">ninety-nine</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَعْجَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">ewe(s)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلِىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">while I have</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَعْجَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">ewe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٲحِدَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">one;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَقَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so he said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَكْفِلْنِيهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Entrust her to me,`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَزَّنِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and he overpowered me</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar qura