<p class="ayah 38-24" id="24" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَقَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Certainly,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ظَلَمَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he has wronged you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِسُؤَالِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">by demanding</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَعْجَتِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your ewe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نِعَاجِهِۦ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">his ewes.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَثِيرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">many</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْخُلَطَآءِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the partners</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَيَبْغِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">certainly oppress</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَعْضُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">one</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[on]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَعْضٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">another</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَمِلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and do</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">righteous deeds</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَلِيلٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and few</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّا هُمْ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) they.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَظَنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And became certain</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">دَاوُۥدُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Dawood</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنَّمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَتَنَّـٰهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We (had) tried him,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱسْتَغْفَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and he asked forgiveness</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) his Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَخَرَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and fell down</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَاكِعًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">bowing</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنَابَ ۩</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and turned in repentance.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>24<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
