s="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَٱلْفُجَّارِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">like the wicked?</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>28<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 38-29" id="29" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كِتَـٰبٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(This is) a Book</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنزَلْنَـٰهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We have revealed it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَيْكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to you,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُبَـٰرَكٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">blessed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّيَدَّبَّرُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that they may ponder</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَايَـٰتِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(over) its Verses</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلِيَتَذَكَّرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and may be reminded</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُوْلُواْ ٱلْأَلْبَـٰبِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those of understanding.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>29<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
