<p class="ayah 38-31" id="31" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">When</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عُرِضَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">were displayed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْعَشِىِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in the afternoon</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّـٰفِنَـٰتُ ٱلْجِيَادُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">excellent bred steeds.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>31<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 38-32" id="32" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَقَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And he said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنِّىٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Indeed, I</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَحْبَبْتُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[I] preferred</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حُبَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) love</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْخَيْرِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the good</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذِكْرِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) remembrance</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) my Lord.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَتَّىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Until</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَوَارَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they were hidden</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْحِجَابِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in the veil;</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>32<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 38-33" id="33" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رُدُّوهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Return them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىَّ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to me.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَطَفِقَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then he began</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَسْحَۢا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to pass (his hand)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلسُّوقِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">over the legs</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْأَعْنَاقِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the necks.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>33<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
