<p class="ayah 38-35" id="35" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`O my Lord!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱغْفِرْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Forgive</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">me</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهَبْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and grant</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">me</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُلْكًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a kingdom,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَنۢبَغِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will) belong</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِأَحَدٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to anyone</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنۢ بَعْدِىٓ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">after me.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, You</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنتَ</span><span c